android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.info: use the authentication credentials of an account
android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.description: Allows an application to request authentication tokens.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to read the sync settings, such as whether sync is enabled for Contacts.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

com.justmoveapp.permission.C2D_MESSAGE.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

playstore_details.title: Just Move - Fitness Motivation
playstore_details.description:
Just Move helps you get fitter with peer pressure. Keep track of your daily steps and weight, interact with like-minded people, turn fitness into a conversation with colleagues and get noticed. 

Get health and fitness tips to learn simple, effective physical exercises, and daily reminders to help you stay motivated and active through the day. We have integrated the Google Fit app and Fitbit to make it convenient and hassle free to count steps. 

Get your company to sign-up to a private environment on Just Move where teams and employees compete with one another on steps and weight. 

♥KEEP TRACK OF YOUR WEIGHT & HOW MANY STEPS YOU TAKE EACH DAY - with the help of the integrated Google Fit app or devices such as Fitbit, Just Move tracks your daily steps and motivates you to fit more physical activity in your day. Simply carry your smartphone with you as you move. You can input your weight and benchmark your BMI against peers. 
 
♥GET A PERSONAL FITNESS BUDDY - Sonya is your fitness buddy on Just Move. By connecting to the Google Fit app, Just Move tracks your daily steps and weight. You are assigned a daily goal and motivated you to walk more and be more active. Sonya appreciates you when you do well and reminds you when you lag behind your fitness goals. She'll help you stay on top of your fitness goals through health and fitness tips, diet and nutrition quizzes and other relevant information.

♥CREATE A COMPANY CHALLENGE AND GIVE FITNESS REWARDS TO EMPLOYEES  Just Move helps HR create energy in the workplace by creating exciting fitness challenges for employees. Just Move helps HRs provide a variety of rewards such as contribution to charity, discounts and badges as employees reach fitness milestones. 

♥SHARE YOUR FITNESS JOURNEYS - Join the Just Move community and share your best health & fitness tips, inspiring photos, fitness selfies after a great run or a photo of your healthy meal. Invite your real life fitness buddies to join you on Just Move, and make fitness more fun together. See your physical exercise regime improve with the support and cheers of the Just Move community!

♥ LEAD A MOVEMENT - Life’s not just about counting your steps. If you are passionate about a cause or would like to celebrate an event or person, start a movement on Just Move and invite others to pledge each step in support. For the fitness minded, Just Move movements offer you the opportunity to start a running group, walking group or fitness, health or general wellness movements. Walk and run together with like-minded enthusiasts - there’s even a leaderboard for some “healthy” competition.

Track. Explore. Interact. Let's get you moving with Just Move! 
- from the developers of WalkOn, winner of IHW Awards 2015.
playstore_details.summary: Track. Share. Interact. Get Rewarded. Stay Motivated. Be Healthy and Fit.
